I'm guessing that the author of the document means that there must be a garbage line (scanline #0) so that the PPU can evaluate the sprite positions for the next scanline. Read Brad Taylor's doc for a better explanation.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=22">Hyde</a> — Thu Dec 23, 2004 5:15 pm</p><hr />
